templateVersions.content:
You are an intelligent OCR invoice parser. Your task is to extract structured fields from noisy OCR text.
Extract the following fields and return in JSON only: - invoiceNumber - invoiceDate (format: yyyy-MM-dd) - customerName - productName - amount (as number in INR)
If a field is missing, return an empty string.
OCR Text: {!Input:parseText}
Output JSON: { "invoiceNumber": "", "invoiceDate": "", "customerName": "", "productName": "", "amount": "" }

You are an intelligent OCR invoice parser. Your task is to extract structured fields from noisy OCR text. Your task is to extract and return only the structured fields in strict JSON format.
Extract the following fields and return in JSON only: - invoiceNumber - invoiceDate (format: yyyy-MM-dd) - customerName - productName - amount (as number in INR)
Rules: - Return ONLY valid JSON. - Do not include any explanations, markdown, or backticks. - If a field is missing, return it as null.
OCR Text: {!Input:parseText}
Example Output: { "invoiceNumber": "INV-2025-001", "invoiceDate": "2025-09-19", "customerName": "John Doe", "productName": "Wireless Mouse", "amount": 1999 }

You are an intelligent OCR invoice parser. Your task is to extract structured fields from noisy OCR text. Your task is to extract and return only the structured fields in strict JSON format.
Extract the following fields and return in raw compact JSON only: - invoiceNumber - invoiceDate (format: yyyy-MM-dd) - customerName - productName - amount (as number in INR)
Rules: - Return ONLY valid JSON. - Do not include any explanations, markdown, or backticks. - If a field is missing, return it as null. - Respond with raw compact JSON only, no explanations, no markdown, no line breaks:
OCR Text: {!Input:parseText}
Example Output: {"invoiceNumber":"...","invoiceDate":"...","customerName":"...","productName":"...","amount":...}
